title: Lip Smacker Cupcake Lover's Lip Gloss Collection in Zipper Bag Set, 6 Count
description: If you love cupcakes, this collection is for you. Enjoy six scrumptious, cupcake-flavored lip glosses that moisturize your lips. Deliciously! It's perfect for any occasion when you want to add flavor and fun. Cupcake-shaped bag is so cute you'll want to take it everywhere you go! Includes Lip Smackers in: Red Velvet, Salted Caramel, Berry Buttercream, Birthday Cake, Strawberry Sprinkle, Vanilla Coconut.
